Reference documentation: 
  https://nifi.apache.org/docs/nifi-docs/html/getting-started.html#downloading-and-installing-nifi

Installation MACOSx

download http://mirror.cc.columbia.edu/pub/software/apache/nifi/0.7.3/nifi-0.7.3-bin.tar.gz

Unpack package
```
gunzip -c nifi-0.7.3-bin.tar.gz | tar xopf -
```

Running in development mode
```
cd nifi-0.7.3/
./bin/nifi.sh start

open http://localhost:8080/nifi
``` 

Stopping in development mode
```
./bin/nifi.sh stop.
```